{"bare_answer": "# Solidity 中未初始化的 Mapping 值\n\n## 默认值规则\n\nSolidity 中所有未初始化的变量都有**零值（zero value）**，mapping 也不例外：\n\n```solidity\nmapping(address => uint256) public balances;\nmapping(address => bool)    public isAdmin;\nmapping(address => address) public referrer;\n\n// 访问任意未设置的 key，返回对应类型的零值：\n// balances[anyAddress] → 0\n// isAdmin[anyAddress]  → false\n// referrer[anyAddress] → address(0)\n```\n\n---\n\n## 常见 Bug 分析\n\n### Bug 1：权限检查绕过\n\n```solidity\n// ❌ 危险写法\ncontract VulnerableAuth {\n    mapping(address => bool) public banned;\n    \n    function withdraw() external {\n        // 逻辑本意：未被封禁才能提款\n        // 实际上：任何地址默认 false，所有人都能通过\n        require(!banned[msg.sender], \"Banned\");\n        // ... 转账逻辑\n    }\n}\n\n// ✅ 正确写法：改用白名单\ncontract SafeAuth {\n    mapping(address => bool) public allowed;\n    \n    function withdraw() external {\n        require(allowed[msg.sender], \"Not allowed\"); // 默认 false = 拒绝\n        // ... 转账逻辑\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Bug 2：余额凭空提取\n\n```solidity\n// ❌ 危险写法\ncontract VulnerableBank {\n    mapping(address => uint256) public balances;\n    \n    function withdraw(uint256 amount) external {\n        // 未存款的用户 balances[msg.sender] = 0\n        // 但如果后续逻辑有误，可能绕过检查\n        require(balances[msg.sender] >= amount, \"Insufficient\");\n        \n        // 先转账后扣款（重入漏洞 + 未初始化组合）\n        (bool ok,) = msg.sender.call{value: amount}(\"\");\n        require(ok);\n        balances[msg.sender] -= amount; // 0 - amount → underflow（旧版本）\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### Bug 3：嵌套 Mapping 的误判\n\n```solidity\n// ❌ 误解：以为可以判断 key 是否存在\ncontract WrongExistCheck {\n    mapping(address => mapping(uint256 => uint256)) public orders;\n    \n    function hasOrder(address user, uint256 orderId) public view returns (bool) {\n        // 永远无法区分\"订单值为0\"和\"订单不存在\"！\n        return orders[user][orderId] != 0; // ❌ 不可靠\n    }\n}\n\n// ✅ 正确写法：用额外字段标记存在性\ncontract CorrectExistCheck {\n    struct Order {\n        uint256 amount;\n        bool exists", "with_skil