ANTLE-Q11", "category": "Mantle", "skill_id": "mantle/mantle-data-indexer", "ground_truth": "Endpoints are runtime inputs. If an endpoint is missing, the skill should request it explicitly instead of guessing.", "question_text": "If I have not configured a Mantle subgraph endpoint yet, what should the data indexer do?", "provider": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"}
