{"bare_answer": "# Mantle Token Swap Execution Plan\n\n## ⚠️ Important Disclaimers First\n- This is **educational/technical guidance only**, not financial advice\n- Verify all contract addresses independently before any transaction\n- Test with small amounts first\n- Smart contract interactions carry real financial risk\n\n---\n\n## Phase 1: Pre-Execution Setup\n\n### 1.1 Wallet Preparation\n```\n□ Hardware wallet connected (Ledger/Trezor recommended)\n□ MetaMask or compatible wallet configured\n□ Mantle Network added to wallet:\n  - Network Name: Mantle\n  - RPC URL: https://rpc.mantle.xyz\n  - Chain ID: 5000\n  - Symbol: MNT\n  - Explorer: https://explorer.mantle.xyz\n```\n\n### 1.2 Balance Verification\n```\n□ Sufficient MNT for gas fees (keep buffer ~0.01-0.05 MNT)\n□ Token you're swapping is in wallet\n□ Token contract address verified on explorer\n□ No pending transactions in queue\n```\n\n---\n\n## Phase 2: Platform Selection\n\n### Primary DEX Options on Mantle\n| Platform | Type | Notes |\n|----------|------|-------|\n| Agni Finance | AMM (Uniswap v3 fork) | Highest liquidity |\n| FusionX | AMM | Native Mantle DEX |\n| Merchant Moe | AMM | LB protocol |\n| iZiSwap | Concentrated liquidity | Good for stables |\n\n### Selection Criteria\n```\n□ Check liquidity depth for your token pair\n□ Compare price impact across platforms\n□ Verify platform is audited\n□ Check if aggregator (e.g., OpenOcean) gives better rate\n```\n\n---\n\n## Phase 3: Pre-Swap Checks\n\n### 3.1 Token Verification\n```bash\n# Verify token contract on Mantle Explorer\nhttps://explorer.mantle.xyz/token/[CONTRACT_ADDRESS]\n\nCheck:\n□ Contract is verified\n□ Token name/symbol matches\n□ No honeypot indicators\n□ Liquidity is locked or substantial\n□ No suspicious transfer restrictions\n```\n\n### 3.2 Price Impact Assessment\n```\nAcceptable thresholds (general guidance):\n< 0.1%  → Low impact, proceed normally\n0.1-1%  → Moderate, acceptable for most\n1-3%    → High, consider splitting order