uts:\n\n1. `wallet_address`: The address of the wallet you want to analyze.\n2. `network`: Specify the network, which can be either `mainnet` or `sepolia`.\n3. Optional: Token/spender scope, if applicable.\n\nOnce these inputs are confirmed, you can proceed to validate the requested wallet and chain context.", "skill_found": true, "question_id": "MANTLE-Q39", "category": "Mantle", "skill_id": "mantle/mantle-portfolio-analyst", "ground_truth": "Use mantle_validateAddress before the read-only queries. Validate wallet, token, and spender addresses instead of guessing. If addresses are invalid, the workflow should not proceed as if they were trusted.", "question_text": "What should happen before querying a wallet, token, or spender address in the portfolio analyst?", "provider": "openai/gpt-4o-mini"}
