{"bare_answer": "# Cairo 合约存储变量声明\n\n## 基本语法（Cairo 1.x / Starknet）\n\n在 Cairo 1.x 中，存储变量通过 **`#[storage]` 结构体**来声明：\n\n```rust\n#[storage]\nstruct Storage {\n    // 简单值类型\n    balance: u256,\n    owner: ContractAddress,\n    counter: u64,\n    \n    // 布尔类型\n    is_active: bool,\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 完整合约示例\n\n```rust\n#[starknet::contract]\nmod MyContract {\n    use starknet::ContractAddress;\n\n    #[storage]\n    struct Storage {\n        // 单值存储\n        total_supply: u256,\n        owner: ContractAddress,\n        \n        // Map 映射类型\n        balances: LegacyMap::<ContractAddress, u256>,\n        \n        // 嵌套 Map\n        allowances: LegacyMap::<(ContractAddress, ContractAddress), u256>,\n    }\n\n    #[external(v0)]\n    fn get_balance(self: @ContractState, account: ContractAddress) -> u256 {\n        // 读取存储\n        self.balances.read(account)\n    }\n\n    #[external(v0)]\n    fn set_balance(ref self: ContractState, account: ContractAddress, amount: u256) {\n        // 写入存储\n        self.balances.write(account, amount);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 存储操作方法\n\n| 操作 | 语法 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **读取** | `self.variable.read()` | 不可变引用 `@ContractState` |\n| **写入** | `self.variable.write(value)` | 可变引用 `ref ContractState` |\n| **Map 读取** | `self.map.read(key)` | 传入键值 |\n| **Map 写入** | `self.map.write(key, value)` | 传入键值对 |\n\n---\n\n## 关键规则\n\n```rust\n// ✅ 读取函数 - 使用不可变引用\nfn read_data(self: @ContractState) -> u64 {\n    self.counter.read()\n}\n\n// ✅ 写入函数 - 使用可变引用 ref\nfn write_data(ref self: ContractState, value: u64) {\n    self.counter.write(value);\n}\n```\n\n> **注意**：`Storage` 结构体名称**必须**固定为 `Storage`，且只能有**一个** `#[storage]` 标注的结构体。", "with_skill_answer": "## Cairo 合约存储变量声明\n\n在 StarkNet 的 Cairo 合约中，存储变量在 `#[storage]` 标注的结构体中声明：\n\n```cairo\n#[starknet::contract]\nmod MyContract {\n    #[storage]\n    struct Storage {\n        // 基本类型\n        owner: starknet::ContractAddress,\n        balance: u256,\n        counter: u64,\n        is_active: bool,\n\n        // Map（单键）\n        balances: starknet::storage::Map<starknet::ContractAddress, u256>,\n\n        // Map（多键嵌套）\n        allowances: starknet::storage::Map<\n            (starknet::ContractAddress, starknet::ContractAddress),\n            u256\n        >,\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 读写存储变量\n\n```cairo\n#[abi(embed_v0)]\nimpl MyImpl of super::IMyContract<ContractState> {\n    fn set_counter(ref self: ContractState, value: u64) {\n        // 写入\n        self.counter.write(value);\n    }\n\n    fn get_counter(self: @ContractState) -> u64 {\n        // 读取\n        self.counter.read()\n    }\n\n    fn get_balance(self: @ContractState, addr: ContractAddress) -> u256 {\n        // Map 读取\n        self.balances.read(addr)\n    }\n\n    fn set_balance(ref self: ContractState, addr: ContractAddress, amount: u256) {\n        // Map 写入\n        self.balances.write(addr, amount);\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 关键规则\n\n| 规则 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| 结构体名必须是 `Storage` | 编译器强制要求 |\n| 标注必须是 `#[storage]` | 缺少则不会生成存储布局 |\n| 不可变引用用 `self: @ContractState` | 只读函数 |\n| 可变引用用 `ref self: ContractState` | 写入函数 |\n| `Map` 路径 | `starknet::storage::Map` |", "skill_found": true, "question_id": "Q1016", "category": "STARKNET", "skill_id": "starknet/cairo-contract-authoring", "ground_truth": "Storage variables are declared using the 'storage' keyword. | The syntax for declaring a storage variable is 'let variable_name: Type = initial_value;'.", "question_text": "在 StarkNet 的 Cairo 合约中，如何声明一个存储变量？请给出正确的语法。", "provider": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"}
