ithub.com/aave/aave-v3-core)", "skill_found": true, "question_id": "Q1051", "category": "ETH", "skill_id": "protocols/aave-v3-integration", "ground_truth": "Aave V3 introduces a new 'flashLoan' function that allows for multiple assets in a single transaction. | V3 supports cross-chain flash loans, which were not available in V2.", "question_text": "Aave V3 与 Aave V2 在闪电贷的实现上有哪些主要区别？", "provider": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"}
