{"bare_answer": "# 使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行本地测试\n\n## 环境搭建\n\n### 安装依赖\n\n```bash\nnpm init -y\nnpm install --save-dev @ton/sandbox @ton/ton @ton/core @ton/crypto jest ts-jest typescript\nnpm install @tact-lang/compiler\n```\n\n### 配置文件\n\n**`tsconfig.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"compilerOptions\": {\n    \"target\": \"ES2020\",\n    \"module\": \"commonjs\",\n    \"strict\": true,\n    \"esModuleInterop\": true,\n    \"outDir\": \"./dist\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**`jest.config.js`**\n```js\nmodule.exports = {\n  preset: \"ts-jest\",\n  testEnvironment: \"node\",\n  testPathPattern: \".*\\\\.spec\\\\.ts$\",\n  globalSetup: \"./jest.setup.js\",\n};\n```\n\n---\n\n## 示例合约\n\n**`contracts/counter.tact`**\n```tact\nimport \"@stdlib/deploy\";\n\nmessage Increment {\n    amount: Int as uint32;\n}\n\nmessage Reset {}\n\ncontract Counter with Deployable {\n    owner: Address;\n    count: Int as uint64;\n\n    init(owner: Address) {\n        self.owner = owner;\n        self.count = 0;\n    }\n\n    receive(msg: Increment) {\n        self.count += msg.amount;\n        emit(LogEventMintRecord{\n            minter: sender(),\n            item_id: self.count,\n            generate_number: msg.amount\n        }.toCell());\n    }\n\n    receive(msg: Reset) {\n        require(sender() == self.owner, \"Only owner can reset\");\n        self.count = 0;\n    }\n\n    get fun count(): Int {\n        return self.count;\n    }\n\n    get fun owner(): Address {\n        return self.owner;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 编译合约\n\n**`tact.config.json`**\n```json\n{\n  \"projects\": [\n    {\n      \"name\": \"Counter\",\n      \"path\": \"contracts/counter.tact\",\n      \"output\": \"build/counter\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n```bash\nnpx tact --config tact.config.json\n```\n\n编译后会生成：\n```\nbuild/counter/\n  ├── counter_Counter.ts       # TypeScript 包装类\n  ├── counter_Counter.abi\n  └── counter_Counter.cell\n```\n\n---\n\n## 编写测试\n\n**`tests/counter.spec.ts`**\n```typescript\nimport { Blockchain, SandboxContract, TreasuryWallet } from \"@ton/sandbox\";\nimport { toNano } from \"@ton/core\";\nimport { Counter } from \"../build/counter/counter_Counter\";\nimport \"@ton/test-utils\"; // 扩展 Jest 匹配器\n\ndescribe(\"Counter Contract\", () => {\n  // ─── 公共变量 ───────────────────────────────────────\n  let blockchain: Blockchain;\n  let owner: SandboxContract<TreasuryWallet>;\n  let user: SandboxContract", "with_skill_answer": "# 使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行本地测试\n\n## 基本流程\n\n### 1. 安装依赖\n\n```bash\nnpm install --save-dev @ton/sandbox @ton/ton @ton/core jest ts-jest\n```\n\n### 2. 典型项目结构\n\n```\ncontracts/\n  counter.tact\ntests/\n  counter.spec.ts\n```\n\n### 3. 编写 Tact 合约示例\n\n```tact\n// contracts/counter.tact\ncontract Counter {\n    val: Int as uint32;\n\n    init(initial: Int) {\n        self.val = initial;\n    }\n\n    receive(\"increment\") {\n        self.val += 1;\n    }\n\n    get fun value(): Int {\n        return self.val;\n    }\n}\n```\n\n### 4. 编写测试文件\n\n```typescript\n// tests/counter.spec.ts\nimport { Blockchain, SandboxContract, TreasuryWallet } from \"@ton/sandbox\";\nimport { toNano } from \"@ton/core\";\nimport { Counter } from \"../build/Counter/tact_Counter\"; // 编译产物\n\ndescribe(\"Counter\", () => {\n  let blockchain: Blockchain;\n  let deployer: SandboxContract<TreasuryWallet>;\n  let counter: SandboxContract<Counter>;\n\n  beforeEach(async () => {\n    // 创建本地沙箱区块链\n    blockchain = await Blockchain.create();\n\n    // 创建有余额的测试钱包\n    deployer = await blockchain.treasury(\"deployer\");\n\n    // 部署合约\n    counter = blockchain.openContract(\n      await Counter.fromInit(0n) // 初始值为 0\n    );\n\n    const deployResult = await counter.send(\n      deployer.getSender(),\n      { value: toNano(\"0.05\") },\n      { $$type: \"Deploy\", queryId: 0n }\n    );\n\n    expect(deployResult.transactions).toHaveTransaction({\n      from: deployer.address,\n      to: counter.address,\n      deploy: true,\n      success: true,\n    });\n  });\n\n  it(\"should increment counter\", async () => {\n    // 调用 receive(\"increment\")\n    const result = await counter.send(\n      deployer.getSender(),\n      { value: toNano(\"0.01\") },\n      \"increment\"\n    );\n\n    expect(result.transactions).toHaveTransaction({\n      from: deployer.address,\n      to: counter.address,\n      success: true,\n    });\n\n    // 调用 getter\n    const val = await counter.getValue();\n    expect(val).toBe(1n);\n  });\n});\n```\n\n---\n\n## 关键 API 说明\n\n| API | 用途 |\n|-----|------|\n| `Blockchain.create()` | 创建本地沙箱环境 |\n| `blockchain.treasury(\"name\")` | 创建预充值测试账户 |\n| `blockchain.openContract()` | 包装合约实例以便交互 |\n| `contract.send(sender, opts, msg)` | 发送内部消息", "skill_found": true, "question_id": "TON-Q46", "category": "TON", "skill_id": "ton/tact-dev", "ground_truth": "`import { Blockchain } from \"@ton/sandbox\"; const blockchain = await Blockchain.create(); const deployer = await blockchain.treasury(\"deployer\"); const myContract = blockchain.openContract(await MyContract.fromInit(arg)); await myContract.send(deployer.getSender(), { value: toNano(\"0.05\") }, { $$type: \"Deploy\", queryId: 0n }); const result = await myContract.send(...);` — sandbox 提供完整 TON 模拟环境，支持多账户和消息传递测试。", "question_text": "如何用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行本地测试？", "provider": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-6"}
{"bare_answer": "要使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行本地测试，你可以按照以下步骤进行操作：\n\n### 1. 安装依赖\n\n首先，确保你已经安装了 Node.js 和 npm。然后在你的项目目录中安装 `@ton/sandbox` 和其他必要的依赖：\n\n```bash\nnpm install @ton/sandbox\n```\n\n### 2. 创建 Tact 合约\n\n编写你的 Tact 合约代码，并保存为 `.tact` 文件。例如，创建一个名为 `MyContract.tact` 的文件：\n\n```tact\ncontract MyContract {\n    // 合约逻辑\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 编译合约\n\n使用 Tact 编译器编译你的合约。确保你已经安装了 Tact 编译器，并在命令行中运行以下命令：\n\n```bash\ntact compile MyContract.tact\n```\n\n这将生成合约的 ABI 和字节码。\n\n### 4. 设置 Sandbox\n\n在你的项目中创建一个 JavaScript 文件，例如 `test.js`，并设置 `@ton/sandbox`：\n\n```javascript\nconst { Sandbox } = require('@ton/sandbox');\n\n(async () => {\n    // 创建一个 Sandbox 实例\n    const sandbox = new Sandbox();\n\n    // 启动 Sandbox\n    await sandbox.start();\n\n    // 部署合约\n    const contractAddress = await sandbox.deploy('MyContract', {\n        // 传入构造函数参数\n    });\n\n    console.log(`合约已部署到地址: ${contractAddress}`);\n\n    // 调用合约方法\n    const result = await sandbox.call(contractAddress, 'methodName', {\n        // 传入方法参数\n    });\n\n    console.log(`方法调用结果: ${result}`);\n\n    // 停止 Sandbox\n    await sandbox.stop();\n})();\n```\n\n### 5. 运行测试\n\n在命令行中运行你的测试文件：\n\n```bash\nnode test.js\n```\n\n### 6. 查看结果\n\n在控制台中查看合约的部署地址和方法调用的结果。\n\n### 注意事项\n\n- 确保你的合约逻辑正确，并且所有依赖的库都已安装。\n- 根据需要调整合约方法的参数和调用方式。\n- 你可以使用 `sandbox` 提供的其他功能，例如模拟交易、查询状态等。\n\n通过以上步骤，你可以在本地环境中使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行测试。", "with_skill_answer": "要使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对 Tact 合约进行本地测试，您可以按照以下步骤进行操作：\n\n1. **安装 @ton/sandbox**：确保您已经安装了 `@ton/sandbox`。可以通过 npm 安装：\n   ```bash\n   npm install @ton/sandbox\n   ```\n\n2. **编写 Tact 合约**：创建一个 Tact 合约文件，例如 `MyContract.tact`，并编写您的合约逻辑。\n\n3. **启动 Sandbox**：在终端中启动 TON Sandbox：\n   ```bash\n   npx ton-sandbox\n   ```\n\n4. **部署合约**：使用 Sandbox 提供的接口将您的 Tact 合约部署到本地环境中。您可以通过 Sandbox 的命令行或 API 来完成这一操作。\n\n5. **进行测试**：一旦合约部署成功，您可以通过调用合约的方法来进行测试。可以使用 JavaScript 或 TypeScript 通过 `@ton/ton` SDK 与合约进行交互。\n\n6. **查看日志和结果**：在 Sandbox 中，您可以查看合约的执行日志和状态，以便调试和验证合约的行为。\n\n通过上述步骤，您可以在本地环境中使用 `@ton/sandbox` 对